keyMappings:
# Insert your preferred key mappings here.
map gw LinkHints.activateMode
map gW LinkHints.activateModeToOpenInNewTab
map <space>[ previousTab
map <space>] nextTab
map K scrollPageUp
map J scrollPageDown
unmap ^
map <space><space> visitPreviousTab
